637, en, 4</unstructured_citation></citation><citation key="ref12"><unstructured_citation>Indel%20detection%20from%20RNA-seq%20data:%20tool%20evaluation%20and%20strategies%20for%20accurate%20detection%20of%20actionable%20mutations, Sun,%20Zhifu%20and%20Bhagwate,%20Aditya%20and%20Prodduturi,%20Naresh%20and%20Yang,%20Ping%20and%20Kocher,%20Jean-Pierre%20A, Driver%20somatic%20mutations%20are%20a%20hallmark%20of%20a%20tumor%20that%20can%20be%20used%20for%20diagnosis%20and%20targeted%20therapy.%20Mutations%20are%20primarily%20detected%20from%20tumor%20DNA.%20As%20dynamic%20molecules%20of%20gene%20activities,%20transcriptome%20profiling%20by%20RNA%20sequence%20(RNA-seq)%20is%20becoming%20increasingly%20popular,%20which%20not%20only%20measures%20gene%20expression%20but%20also%20structural%20variations%20such%20as%20mutations%20and%20fusion%20transcripts.%20Although%20single-nucleotide%20variants%20(SNVs)%20can%20be%20easily%20identified%20from%20RNA-seq,%20intermediate%20long%20insertions/deletions%20(indels%20%3E%202%20bases%20and%20less%20than%20sequence%20reads)%20cause%20significant%20challenges%20and%20are%20ignored%20by%20most%20RNA-seq%20analysis%20tools.%20This%20study%20evaluates%20commonly%20used%20RNA-seq%20analysis%20programs%20along%20with%20variant%20and%20somatic%20mutation%20callers%20in%20a%20series%20of%20data%20sets%20with%20simulated%20and%20known%20indels.%20The%20aim%20is%20to%20develop%20strategies%20for%20accurate%20indel%20detection.%20Our%20results%20show%20that%20the%20RNA-seq%20alignment%20is%20the%20most%20important%20step%20for%20indel%20identification%20and%20the%20evaluated%20programs%20have%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20sensitivity%20to%20map%20sequence%20reads%20with%20indels,%20from%20not%20at%20all%20to%20decently%20sensitive.%20The%20sensitivity%20is%20impacted%20by%20sequence%20read%20lengths.%20Most%20variant%20calling%20programs%20rely%20on%20hard%20evidence%20indels%20marked%20in%20the%20alignment%20and%20the%20programs%20with%20realignment%20may%20use%20soft-clipped%20reads%20for%20indel%20inferencing.%20Based%20on%20the%20observations,%20we%20have%20provided%20practical%20recommendations%20for%20indel%20detection%20when%20different%20RNA-seq%20aligners%20are%20used%20and%20demonstrated%20the%20best%20option%20with%20highly%20reliable%20results.%20With%20careful%20customization%20of%20bioinformatics%20algorithms,%20RNA-seq%20can%20be%20reliably%20used%20for%20both%20SNV%20and%20indel%20mutation%20detection%20that%20can%20be%20used%20for%20clinical%20decision-making., Brief.%20Bioinform., jul, 2016, http://dx.doi.org/10.1093/bib/bbw069, EGFR;%20RNA%20sequencing;%20alignment;%20indels;%20mutation;%20variant%20calling, en, 7</unstructured_citation></citation><citation key="ref13"><unstructured_citation>Degust:%20Powerfull%20and%20user%20friendly%20front-end%20data%20analsysis,%20visualisation%20and%20exploratory%20tool%20for%20RNA-sequencing, Powell,%20David, sep, 2015, github, http://degust.erc.monash.edu, 9</unstructured_citation></citation><citation key="ref14"><unstructured_citation>Broadinstitute, Picard-Tools, broadinstitute, http://broadinstitute.github.io/picard</unstructured_citation></citation><citation key="ref15"><unstructured_citation>Integrative%20genomics%20viewer, Robinson,%20James%20T%20and%20Thorvaldsd%C3%B3ttir,%20Helga%20and%20Winckler,%20Wendy%20and%20Guttman,%20Mitchell%20and%20Lander,%20Eric%20S%20and%20Getz,%20Gad%20and%20Mesirov,%20Jill%20P, Nat.%20Biotechnol., Nature%20Publishing%20Group,%20a%20division%20of%20Macmillan%20Publishers%20Limited.%20All%20Rights%20Reserved., 29, 24, jan, 2011, http://dx.doi.org/10.1038/nbt.1754, 1</unstructured_citation></citation></citation_list>
